nodes.text: Ragmar V was a barren, desert-coated world in the Outer Rim Territories. Its population center was an outpost of outcasts of various species, including Humans, Klatooinians, Bith, Rodians, Ithorians, Gamorreans, Jawas, and Devaronians.
At the very end of the Clone Wars, a force under Jedi General Sev sought to establish a staging area on the world. The attempt was interrupted by the execution of Order 66.
